<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 19 at 9:25AM MST  by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>Areas of light snow are developing across the HiLine this morning.
Expect new snow accumulations of a Trace to one-half inch, with
isolated higher amounts under narrow snow bands. Light snow will
continue, at times, through today and overnight. Be prepared for
variable driving conditions.</description>
